        "term": "Senior Tech",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 263,
        "end_idx": 274
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "My battery went bad about a year and a half after having it and it cost around eighty to a hundred dollars!",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "battery",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 3,
        "end_idx": 10
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The screen is bright and clear, the operating system is solid and friendly to a novice.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "screen",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 4,
        "end_idx": 10
      },
      {
        "term": "operating system",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 36,
        "end_idx": 52
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": " THE MOTHERBOARD IS DEAD !",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "MOTHERBOARD",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 5,
        "end_idx": 16
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "See when it comes to laptops you buy it and get just a normal operating system with trials of must need stuff that should come with it.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "operating system",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 62,
        "end_idx": 78
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "For those that care about noise this thing doesn't really make any;",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "noise",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 26,
        "end_idx": 31
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "And if you do a lot of writing, editing is a problem since there is no  forward delete  key.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "delete  key",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 80,
        "end_idx": 91
      },
      {
        "term": "editing",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 32,
        "end_idx": 39
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Additional caveat: the base installation comes with some Toshiba-specific software that may or may not be to a user's liking.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "base installation",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 23,
        "end_idx": 40
      },
      {
        "term": "software",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 74,
        "end_idx": 82
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "-Called headquarters again, they report that TFT panel is broken, should be fixed by the end of the week (week 3).",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "TFT panel",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 45,
        "end_idx": 54
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The Bluetooth was not there at all, and the fingerprint reader driver would be there, but the software would hang after installation was 1/2 way done.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "Bluetooth",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 4,
        "end_idx": 13
      },
      {
        "term": "fingerprint reader driver",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 44,
        "end_idx": 69
      },
      {
        "term": "software",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 94,
        "end_idx": 102
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The service tech said he had tried to duplicate the damage and wasn't able to recreate it therefore it had to be their defect.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "service tech",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 4,
        "end_idx": 16
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I can barely use any usb devices because they will not stay connected properly.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "usb devices",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 21,
        "end_idx": 32
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I've also had to have the keyboard replaced at my expense.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "keyboard",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 26,
        "end_idx": 34
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Great value, fast delivery- Computer works as if brand new, no problems, very pleased",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "delivery",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 18,
        "end_idx": 26
      },
      {
        "term": "value",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 6,
        "end_idx": 11
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Though the picture, video, and music software is nowhere close to professional grade software Im used to (CS5) but does the job for beginner and even intermediate media designers.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "music software",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 31,
        "end_idx": 45
      },
      {
        "term": "software",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 85,
        "end_idx": 93
      },
      {
        "term": "picture",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 11,
        "end_idx": 18
      },
      {
        "term": "video",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 20,
        "end_idx": 25
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Ease of use is just one of the benefits I love about my Mac.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "use",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 8,
        "end_idx": 11
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Not sure how I recommend it for quality gaming, as I have a desktop rig for that reason.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "gaming",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 40,
        "end_idx": 46
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "A month or so ago, the freaking motherboard just died.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "motherboard",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 32,
        "end_idx": 43
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I bought a cordless mouse for it, but don't always take it out;",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "cordless mouse",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 11,
        "end_idx": 25
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "oh yeah, and if the fancy webcam breaks guess who you have to send it to to get it fixed?",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "webcam",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 26,
        "end_idx": 32
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Quality Display  I love HP,, it's the only computer/printer we will buy.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "Quality Display",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 0,
        "end_idx": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "(If you ever see the spinning beachball come up when you think it shouldn't, check the \"Activity Monitor\" app to see if the disk throughput has temporarily dropped to zero.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "disk throughput",
        "polarity": 1,
