        "end_idx": 139
      },
      {
        "term": "spinning beachball",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 21,
        "end_idx": 39
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I also like the acer arcade but these were reallythe only two things I liked about this laptop.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "acer arcade",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 16,
        "end_idx": 27
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "  i have tried to charge on different batteries with no luck.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "batteries",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 38,
        "end_idx": 47
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "  This process continued to repeat itself until the mother board had been replaced 4 times and the hard drive replaced 3 times.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "mother board",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 52,
        "end_idx": 64
      },
      {
        "term": "hard drive",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 99,
        "end_idx": 109
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I love the multi-touch trackpad.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "multi-touch trackpad",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 11,
        "end_idx": 31
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The So called laptop Runs to Slow and I hate it!",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "Runs",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 21,
        "end_idx": 25
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I also love the design, the looks, the feel, and the my toshiba feature is wonderfull.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "design",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 16,
        "end_idx": 22
      },
      {
        "term": "looks",
