        "end_idx": 43
      },
      {
        "term": "my toshiba feature",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 53,
        "end_idx": 71
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Comfterbale to use light easy to transport.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "use",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 15,
        "end_idx": 18
      },
      {
        "term": "transport",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 33,
        "end_idx": 42
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Product support very poor as each phone call costs me long distan",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "Product support",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 0,
        "end_idx": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "My husband got me this for Chrismas after getting me a very expensve laptop that did not work after 2 days.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "work",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 89,
        "end_idx": 93
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "  The lcd screen stopped working on mine after 10 months.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "lcd screen",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 6,
        "end_idx": 16
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Actually, I had noticed the one on the sales floor also didn't have sound!",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "sound",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 68,
        "end_idx": 73
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, I issued a replacement RMA for a few dead pixels in the upper zone of the screen, which is noticable to me.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "screen",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 80,
        "end_idx": 86
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "OS X is solid with lots of innovations such as quicklook which save heaps of time.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "OS X",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 0,
        "end_idx": 4
      },
      {
        "term": "quicklook",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 47,
        "end_idx": 56
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The next time I had an issue my lightscribe wouldn't work.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "lightscribe",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 32,
        "end_idx": 43
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I also liked the glass screen.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "glass screen",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 17,
        "end_idx": 29
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Once again, I was told it was the suspicious  power supply  problem.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "power supply",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 46,
        "end_idx": 58
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "-I propose that they can just swap the hard drives.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "hard drives",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 39,
        "end_idx": 50
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "There is no need to open a program first and the cliick open or import.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "program",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 27,
        "end_idx": 34
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "It's super fast and a great value for the price!",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "value",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 28,
        "end_idx": 33
      },
      {
        "term": "price",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 42,
        "end_idx": 47
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I took 3-4 years researching brands and prices of laptops.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "prices",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 40,
        "end_idx": 46
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The AMD Turin processor seems to always perform so much better than Intel.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "AMD Turin processor",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 4,
        "end_idx": 23
      },
      {
        "term": "Intel",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 68,
        "end_idx": 73
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Some features arent friendly ( volume wheel, sound quality, etc.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "volume wheel",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 31,
        "end_idx": 43
      },
      {
        "term": "sound quality",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 45,
        "end_idx": 58
      },
      {
        "term": "features",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 5,
        "end_idx": 13
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I had purchased it from a major electronics store and took it to their service department to find out what the problem was.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "service department",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 71,
        "end_idx": 89
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Then after 4 or so months the charger stopped working so I was forced to go out and buy new hardware just to keep this computer running.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "charger",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 30,
        "end_idx": 37
      },
      {
        "term": "hardware",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 92,
        "end_idx": 100
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Overall : Poor, Features: Average, Performance: Poor, Battery Life: Excellent, Price-Value: Poor",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "Features",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 16,
        "end_idx": 24
      },
      {
        "term": "Performance",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 35,
        "end_idx": 46
      },
      {
        "term": "Battery Life",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 54,
        "end_idx": 66
      },
      {
        "term": "Price",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 79,
        "end_idx": 84
      },
      {
        "term": "Value",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 85,
        "end_idx": 90
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "(I had been a Windows/Linux user before this) I love the size because the screen is big enough for what I use it for (Internet, artwork), and yet it is small enough to be reasonably portable.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "size",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 57,
        "end_idx": 61
      },
      {
        "term": "screen",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 74,
        "end_idx": 80
      },
      {
        "term": "Windows",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 14,
        "end_idx": 21
      },
      {
        "term": "Linux",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 22,
        "end_idx": 27
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "It is everything I'd hoped it would be from a look and feel standpoint, but somehow a bit more sturdy.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "look and feel standpoint",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 46,
        "end_idx": 70
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, the biggest problem has been tech support.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "tech support",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 38,
        "end_idx": 50
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Setting would change for some reason, the screen size would change on it's own, like the pixel sizes and whatnot.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "Setting",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 0,
        "end_idx": 7
      },
      {
        "term": "screen size",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 42,
        "end_idx": 53
      },
      {
        "term": "pixel sizes",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 89,
        "end_idx": 100
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The only thing is that the battery won't last more than 1/2 an hour.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "battery",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 27,
        "end_idx": 34
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Its fast and another thing I like is that it has three USB ports.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "USB ports",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 55,
        "end_idx": 64
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I was happy with My purchase of a Toshiba Satellite L305D-S5934 laptop until it came time to have it repaired under the Toshiba Warranty.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "Toshiba Warranty",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 120,
        "end_idx": 136
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "After a couple of years, my battery life began to diminish but was replaced for free due to a company-wide recall of my particular battery.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "battery",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 131,
        "end_idx": 138
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I've haven't had any major problems with the laptop except that the plastic piece that covers the usb port wires have all come off.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "plastic piece",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 68,
        "end_idx": 81
      },
      {
        "term": "usb port wires",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 98,
        "end_idx": 112
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I purchased a Toshiba Satellite M60 (with harman/kardon speakers!) in December of 2005.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "speakers",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 56,
        "end_idx": 64
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The tech guy then said the service center does not do 1-to-1 exchange and I have to direct my concern to the \"sales\" team, which is the retail shop which I bought my netbook from.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "service center",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 27,
        "end_idx": 41
      },
      {
        "term": "\"sales\" team",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 109,
        "end_idx": 121
      },
      {
        "term": "tech guy",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 4,
        "end_idx": 12
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The PhotoBooth is a great program, it takes very good pictures with the built-in camera.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "PhotoBooth",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 4,
        "end_idx": 14
      },
      {
        "term": "program",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 26,
        "end_idx": 33
      },
      {
        "term": "built-in camera",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 72,
        "end_idx": 87
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "But the quality, in general was less than the worth of the cheap laptop.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "quality",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 8,
        "end_idx": 15
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I would recommend it just because of the internet speed probably because thats the only thing i really care about.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "internet speed",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 41,
        "end_idx": 55
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Charger seems large for this class of computer.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "Charger",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 0,
        "end_idx": 7
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Sure, the initial out of pocket expense is greater, but that should not dissuade anyone from the fact that these machines run like none other on the planet, and when I factor in all the money in that I wasted on Geek Squad and the latest patches to de-corrupt my infested PCs, it probably comes out about even anyhow.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "expense",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 32,
        "end_idx": 39
      },
      {
        "term": "run",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 122,
        "end_idx": 125
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Crisp screen, great battery life, and plenty of storage.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "screen",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 6,
        "end_idx": 12
      },
      {
        "term": "battery life",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 20,
        "end_idx": 32
      },
      {
        "term": "storage",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 48,
        "end_idx": 55
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The fact that the screen reacts to the lighting around you is an added luxury-when you are working around others in dark areas and want privacy or don't want to bother them with bright lighting, it is very convenient to have a darker, softer lit screen.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "screen",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 18,
        "end_idx": 24
      },
      {
        "term": "screen",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 246,
        "end_idx": 252
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "The overall build quality of the unit is excellent and she'd recommend it to anyone else looking for a netbook.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "build quality",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 12,
        "end_idx": 25
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't have stupid pop up windows (even when I have pop ups blocked), I don't have to wait 5 minutes for a webpage to download, and best of all I can run all the web programming software I need to use all at once without slowing me down.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "pop up windows",
        "polarity": 2,
