        "start_idx": 53,
        "end_idx": 60
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "You will need them if you want to reload the OS (I recommend doing if you can to start fresh and optimal).",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "OS",
        "polarity": 1,
        "start_idx": 45,
        "end_idx": 47
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "None of the techs at HP knew what they were doing.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "techs at HP",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 12,
        "end_idx": 23
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "It is easy to use, has great screen quality, and every so light weight.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "screen quality",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 29,
        "end_idx": 43
      },
      {
        "term": "use",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 14,
        "end_idx": 17
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Came fully loaded - good.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "loaded",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 11,
        "end_idx": 17
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Also the display is exceptional!",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "display",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 9,
        "end_idx": 16
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "in May I started having problems with the USB ports not working.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "USB ports",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 42,
        "end_idx": 51
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": " One night I turned the freaking thing off after using it, the next day I turn it on, no GUI, screen all dark, power light steady, hard drive light steady and not flashing as it usually does.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "GUI",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 89,
        "end_idx": 92
      },
      {
        "term": "screen",
