        "end_idx": 122
      },
      {
        "term": "hard drive ligh",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 131,
        "end_idx": 146
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "Not easy to carry.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "carry",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 12,
        "end_idx": 17
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "They say sorry out of warranty.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "warranty",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 22,
        "end_idx": 30
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "A key contributor that led me to Mac is the art aspect.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "art aspect",
        "polarity": 2,
        "start_idx": 44,
        "end_idx": 54
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "text": "It could be a perfect laptop if it would have faster system memory and its radeon 5850 would have DDR5 instead of DDR3.",
    "aspects": [
      {
        "term": "system memory",
        "polarity": 0,
        "start_idx": 53,
        "end_idx": 66
      },
      {
        "term": "radeon 5850",
